msgstr ""
"Skaleer draadsegment-wydte volgens die geskaleerde amplitude-omhullende "
"s(n), sodat sterk gebiede dik teken en nulpunte dun teken."

#: resources/animate.glade:908
msgid "Overlays:"
msgstr "Oorlegs:"

#: resources/animate.glade:919
msgid "Nodes/antinodes"
msgstr "Nodusse/antinodusse"

#: resources/animate.glade:924
msgid ""
"Mark current nulls (plus tick) and peaks (cross tick) on wire segments.\n"
"\n"
"Marks derive from the phase-invariant envelope, so they hold still while the "
"wave animates."
msgstr ""
"Merk stroom-nulpunte (plus-merkie) en pieke (kruis-merkie) op "
"draadsegmente.\n"
"\n"
"Merke word afgelei van die fase-onveranderlike omhullende, sodat hulle "
"stilbly terwyl die golf animeer."

#: resources/animate.glade:935
msgid "Comet"
msgstr "Komeet"

#: resources/animate.glade:940
msgid ""
"Ride a bright head on the instantaneous positive crest so wave motion reads "
